To update website
-----------------

1. Local Build
   `./build.bash`
   when prompted, choose incremental build
   when prompted, choose local links


2. Use browser to inspect `_site/`


3. Remote build
   `./build.bash`
   when prompted, choose incremental build
   when prompted, choose remote links
   when prompted, push gh-pages branch
   when prompoted, push 



To install framework
--------------------

Under macports:
    default macports ruby (1.8) too old
    install ruby environment manager rbenv via macports
    install ruby (2.4) via via rbenv
    install jekyll prerequisites
    install jekyll
    confirm installation via jekyll tutorial



To prepare photos
-----------------

Using Adobe Lightroom:
    crop and adjust raw photos
    organize photos into collections
    export 2000px jpegs into directories

